wt.associativity

Interface EquivalenceBasicControlDelegate


  • public interface EquivalenceBasicControlDelegate
    The purpose of this delegate is to perform validations related to Equivalence link. This interface should be implemented by customized implementations.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
